  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your opponent's advanced training in moving around you is surpassed only by your readiness for it.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Anticipate Dodge, Dodge, Mobility; base attack bonus +9, brawler level 6th, or monk level 6th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Opponents with the Mobility feat do not gain the dodge bonus granted by that feat when they provoke attacks of opportunity by moving out of or within your threatened area.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When an opponent with the Mobility feat moves out of or within your threatened area, you can spend 2 stamina points to gain a +4 bonus on your attack of opportunity.",
